---
import Icon from "./Icon.astro";
---

<section class="box skills">
  <div class="stack gap-2 lg:gap-4">
    <Icon
      icon="terminal-window"
      color="var(--accent-regular)"
      size="2.5rem"
      gradient
    />
    <h2>Frontend Development</h2>
    <p>
      Capable of building modern, responsive and scalable user interfaces using
      technologies like React, Next.js, Astro and TypeScript. Focused on writing
      clean, maintainable code and delivering smooth user experiences through
      efficient component architecture and API integration.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="stack gap-2 lg:gap-4">
    <Icon icon="code" color="var(--accent-regular)" size="2.5rem" gradient />
    <h2>API Integration</h2>
    <p>
      Experience consuming and integrating REST APIs, handling asynchronous
      data, and managing application state effectively.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="stack gap-2 lg:gap-4">
    <Icon icon="trophy" color="var(--accent-regular)" size="2.5rem" gradient />
    <h2>Problem Solving</h2>
    <p>
      Strong ability to analyze problems, break them down into smaller parts,
      and implement effective solutions. Comfortable debugging, researching and
      adapting quckly to new challenges in real-world development scenarios.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="stack gap-2 lg:gap-4">
    <Icon
      icon="strategy"
      color="var(--accent-regular)"
      size="2.5rem"
      gradient
    />
    <h2>Strategic Thinking</h2>
    <p>
      Able to think beyond code by understanding user needs and aligning
      technical decisions with project goals. Focused on building solutions that
      are not only functional, but also meaningful and scalable.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .box {
    border: 1px solid var(--gray-800);
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background-color: var(--gray-999_40);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
  }

  .skills {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 3rem;
  }

  .skills h2 {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
  }

  .skills p {
    color: var(--gray-400);
  }

  @media screen (min-width: 50em) {
    .box {
      border-radius: 1.5rem;
      padding: 2.5rem;
    }

    .skills {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 5rem;
    }

    .skills h2 {
      font-size: var(--text-2xl);
    }
  }
</style>
